    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by high relevance, strong quantitative output comparison results (E/uval < 1.96 across all QoI), and corroborating evidence from two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
